# --- TALA server-side config (added) ---
# Service-role key is used ONLY on the server to read the OpenRouter key + knowledge
# from Supabase. It bypasses RLS, so NEVER expose it to the browser (no VITE_ prefix).
# Get it from: Supabase dashboard → Project Settings → API → service_role key.
